{"tid":876851,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"慎入：）有無人做過類似油脂皮膚痣既切割手術或激光？","createTime":"2018-10-26T02:10:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T15:12:11.000Z","uid":111996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"788997a5f2ddb2f49ead15d0741bd3142dbda2c1","tid":876851,"uid":111996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T02:10:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/26/100555_023598ab585a6b28b954210d137f6c1a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F26%2F100555_023598ab585a6b28b954210d137f6c1a.png&h=be333caa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前濕疹睇醫生，醫生講呢個係油脂皮膚痣。做切除手術或激光，可以預防變癌。<br />\n佢話因爲範圍都大，搞完有疤痕，最好叫我搵埋整容醫生一齊搞。<br />\n所以想知有無咩機構，有埋整容醫生，同埋價錢大概幾錢？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知有無巴絲話到我知。"},{"pid":"16ed4fabb2f03fe01b61fb62d1e31c4a46130cb2","tid":876851,"uid":525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T13:42:16.000Z","msg":"反麻下場"},{"pid":"0f83903277522ce26af3558471eb6057799d88ef","tid":876851,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T14:56:22.000Z","msg":"反麻下場"},{"pid":"d80bff163415d0225f0c1364013042252f26e8e2","tid":876851,"uid":150348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T14:59:21.000Z","msg":"雞"},{"pid":"0a8ebb62d26a98f283d6f20413435a87f0b19b47","tid":876851,"uid":130359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T15:12:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}